{"tid":101000,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩方法可以令自己早d瞓得著","createTime":"2017-01-30T13:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T03:01:15.000Z","uid":69120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"29f45ac6bcfeea86bfd0c4e854e5b0b66c0edc5b","tid":101000,"uid":69120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:09:41.000Z","msg":"成日深夜 2-3 點先瞓得著<br />\n最攰都係最快1點瞓到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞到黑眼圈都幾明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲有咩方法分享下"},{"pid":"f27274e45152add08a23bec0f4f18f3aba105cf5","tid":101000,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:10:32.000Z","msg":"平時幾點起身？"},{"pid":"8306e6800ba80f4d377d6a947a632138f97509b0","tid":101000,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:10:53.000Z","msg":"做運動做到攰"},{"pid":"a210c8b269da8f3a8dd52eda42aa4a43b75bdcd8","tid":101000,"uid":21664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:10:54.000Z","msg":"早D訓落床 唔好放手機喺床邊或太接近自己？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71f8b8d932713337a3503380b36938d1dafbaa3","tid":101000,"uid":58893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:18:46.000Z","msg":"睇字典"},{"pid":"da9e933e2d6f6b59dbe2f300a4cdc062de9b6a09","tid":101000,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:19:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad963991dfeff8ea3652eae0481f96549db28a63","tid":101000,"uid":69120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:40:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時幾點起身？</blockquote><br />\n假期就下就1-2 點先起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早起好難起"},{"pid":"16f85467ea25f3c69faa87beaf68851d2d2effe4","tid":101000,"uid":17958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:51:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平時幾點起身？</blockquote><br />\n假期就下就1-2 點先起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早起好難起</blockquote><br />\n難怪啦咁晏起<br />\n認真早起身夜晚會早瞓"},{"pid":"cf3b9788f7111bf97bd6b2a88a1de00783466731","tid":101000,"uid":54450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:01:15.000Z","msg":"每日早15-30分鐘訓，逐日較早d<br />\n<br />\n鬧鐘較6個鐘後響，因為人既sleep cycle係1.5hrs, 你鍾意可以較7.5, 不過我就6個鐘夠<br />\n<br />\n用電話較鬧鐘放到房既另一邊，等你一定要雙腳掂地先整停到，同時防止睡前玩<br />\n<br />\n起身後飲杯水梳洗，再做運動，因為可以激活你個人，我就做500reps challenge, 可以youtube搵下<br />\n<br />\n之後做你想做既野，讀書，寫blog, 睇一集劇etc, 一定要有呢樣野，咁你會期望早起<br />\n<br />\n之後你就自然會早訓，因為你早起可以做多好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}